        <h2 class="bw-modular__title" style="font-size:clamp(24px, 3vw, 34px);">Layout sets the foundation. Materials and detailing decide how the kitchen performs every day.</h2>
        <p class="bw-modular__copy">Two kitchens can share the same floor plan and still feel very different in durability, maintenance, and finish quality. The choices below are where much of that difference is built.</p>
